description:
Delilah Strong is 5'9 150lbs and full of confidence. She is big, strong, and thinks of her self as pretty tough. Like most new comers she is rudely awakened.
Vendetta is last seasons overall Champion. The only question really is by how much will she win, and how hard will the Succubus get fucked in RD4.
